headline: Marsh McLennan’s Mercer Acquires Hexarem
summary: TORONTO, November 03, 2025--Mercer, a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) and a global leader in helping clients realize their investment objectives, shape the future of work and enhance health and retirement outcomes for their people, today announced that it has acquired Hexarem, a boutique Canadian human resources consulting firm specializing in executive compensation and governance advisory services. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.

headline: Marsh McLennan Agency Acquires Hayden Wood Insurance Agency
summary: WHITE PLAINS, N.Y., November 03, 2025--Marsh McLennan Agency (MMA), a business of Marsh and a leading provider of business insurance, employee health and benefits, retirement and wealth, and private client insurance solutions across the US and Canada, today announced the acquisition of Hayden Wood Insurance Agency Inc., a Southborough, Massachusetts-based independent agency. Terms of the acquisition were not disclosed.
